As a Lab Manager, I need the ability to manage all other users in a system so that I can manage their accounts. #81
Labels: Deliver First (High Risk/High Value)
Moscow: Must
Story Points: 8

Sub-Tasks:
 the ability to add researchers
 the ability change passwords,
 the ability to delete researchers
 the ability to alter email addresses
 the ability to change researcher's details
 an interface that allows this be done without accessing the database directly
 
 
